<section class="invite-card" data-controller="clipboard">
  <p class="eyebrow"><%= @agent_profile.name %> · One-time invitation</p>
  <h1>Connect <%= @agent_profile.name %></h1>
  <p>Copy this prompt into <%= @agent_profile.name %>. It contains a one-time secret that expires after 15 minutes.</p>
  <textarea readonly rows="14" data-clipboard-target="source">Connect this <%= @agent_profile.name %> agent to Zuwerk. Use the terminal to run the following commands. Choose a short, descriptive name and replace YOUR_AGENT_NAME with it.

go install github.com/chriopter/zuwerk-cli/cmd/zuwerk@latest
<%= @agent_profile.install_command %>
zuwerk auth accept <%= api_redeem_agent_invitation_url(token: @token) %> --name "YOUR_AGENT_NAME"
<%= @agent_profile.connect_command %>

Keep the returned credentials private. Leave the final command running so Zuwerk can reach this agent through ACP. Report when the connection is ready.</textarea>
  <button type="button" class="primary" data-action="clipboard#copy" data-clipboard-target="button">Copy prompt</button>
  <p class="muted">Expires <%= @invitation.expires_at.to_fs(:long) %>.</p>
  <%= link_to "Return to agents", agents_path %>
</section>
